svg.title: Sheet Music for "The Blackbird (Step Dance)"

text.tspan: Notes: Really interesting tune I stumbled upon, maybe in the Irish repertoire? I can't make much sense
of it yet; it seems to cut the final phrase by half (seems to fit the step dance form), though
I've seen versions (e.g. DJN) that extend it to a regular 8 bars. I have no idea about the
chording, either -- definitely still a WIP!
